<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="tr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>500 - Sunucu Hatası | Ev Lezzetleri</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/assets/css/main.css">
    <style>
        body { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; min-height: 100vh; margin: 0; font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; background: var(--bg-color, #f8f9fa); }
        .error-container { text-align: center; padding: 2rem; max-width: 480px; }
        .error-code { font-size: 6rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--primary-color, #e74c3c); line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
        .error-title { font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text-color, #2c3e50); margin-bottom: 1rem; }
        .error-msg { color: var(--text-secondary, #636e72); margin-bottom: 2rem; line-height: 1.6; }
        .btn-home { display: inline-block; background: var(--primary-color, #e74c3c); color: #fff; padding: 0.75rem 2rem; border-radius: 8px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500; transition: opacity 0.2s; }
        .btn-home:hover { opacity: 0.85; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="error-container">
        <div class="error-code">500</div>
        <div class="error-title">Sunucu Hatası</div>
        <p class="error-msg">Beklenmedik bir hata oluştu. Ekibimiz bilgilendirildi.<br>Lütfen daha sonra tekrar deneyin.</p>
        <a href="/" class="btn-home">Ana Sayfaya Dön</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
